    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal for someone looking for a major project or a parts donor. The body has extensive rust, particularly along the frame and wheel wells, and the transmission is currently slipping significantly. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and the electronics are inconsistent. It will require a trailer for transport as it is not currently roadworthy.",
